{"tid":1847501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實銀行應該叫人唔好返工","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T10:16:35.000Z","uid":127575,"like":166,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"caf7d6bac8f1bb70c0ed9382f81d443a9117ac29","tid":1847501,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銀行咁撚多廢老排隊<br />\n<br />\n係咪想害死更多員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5e9cf4c02876cc00f0e7e9811a25f1511cb8a5","tid":1847501,"uid":126621,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5M3ShVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5M3ShVs.png&h=9ebbd210&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14543584b6c204e854add31e9bf000944c6f5b29","tid":1847501,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"銀行工會=戇尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0d2f5cf15564b10416b82aaf0045e68daa0ef4","tid":1847501,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b424fd69a86af1e26078524af545ca279f9dad5c","tid":1847501,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3835a3f5416059b365ed034e850abceb19a557bf","tid":1847501,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2a988079b88333ba4fabe5e1620d02a1823d39","tid":1847501,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e45c5d01645b5c80e12680d55ca3e136f99bf07","tid":1847501,"uid":52540,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"做TELLER隔個窗<br />\n<br />\n做CS 開戶口 真係面對面 100%硬食"},{"pid":"09dfc3a34ad4bd212536a2e4a88f348c1ba36690","tid":1847501,"uid":3302,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"好心痛匯豐企門口果d囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n囡囡們一定要冇事"},{"pid":"1cfb48a01bdd1d439fb4f0d93287ba7fee414872","tid":1847501,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:52:42.000Z","msg":"而且好多支那人宜家拎hkid  無人知佢是咪去完武漢返黎"},{"pid":"4dcdba15b3490790bde66a8d83260515baaf491d","tid":1847501,"uid":271,"like":19,"dislike":1,"sco